## 🔹 5. Implementation

```python id="geo123"
import pandas as pd
import folium
from folium.plugins import HeatMap

# Load dataset
df = pd.read_excel("road_accidents_dataset.xlsx")

# Create base map (example coordinates)
map_center = [37.77, -122.42]
m = folium.Map(location=map_center, zoom_start=5)

# Add heatmap
heat_data = [[row['Latitude'], row['Longitude']] for index, row in df.iterrows() if 'Latitude' in df.columns]

if heat_data:
    HeatMap(heat_data).add_to(m)

# Save map
m.save("accident_heatmap.html")
```

